  </head>

 <body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Free Brain Energy Guide</p>

        <h1>Feel Mentally Drained Lately?</h1>

        <p class="subheadline">
          Discover 5 simple ways to restore focus, clarity, and brain energy naturally.
        </p>

        <ul class="benefits">
          <li>Why your brain feels tired even after sleep</li>
          <li>Hidden daily habits that quietly kill focus</li>
          <li>A simple 10-minute brain reset routine</li>
          <li>Foods and nutrients linked to mental clarity</li>
          <li>The overlooked support many people are using today</li>
        </ul>

        <getresponse-form form-id="e9d8986d-1305-419a-96b8-00839003285f" e="1"></getresponse-form>
      </div>

      <div class="visual">
        <div class="guide-card">
          <p class="small">FREE GUIDE</p>
          <h2>The Brain Energy Reset</h2>
          <p>5 simple ways to feel sharper, focused, and mentally energized again.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f4f8fb;
    --dark: #10202f;
    --text: #34495e;
    --muted: #6b7c8f;
    --primary: #1e88e5;
    --primary-dark: #1269b3;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --accent: #20c997;
  }

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .page {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 32px 18px;
  }

  .hero {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1120px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .content {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 48px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(16, 32, 47, 0.08);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(32, 201, 151, 0.12);
    color: #0f8d68;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    color: var(--dark);
    font-size: clamp(38px, 6vw, 64px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
  }

  .subheadline {
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    font-size: 21px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .benefits {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .benefits li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 30px;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .benefits li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .optin {
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background: #f7fbff;
    border: 1px solid #dbeaf5;
  }

  .optin label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--dark);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .optin input {
    width: 100%;
    height: 56px;
    padding: 0 18px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid #c8d9e8;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    outline: none;
  }

  .optin input:focus {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(30, 136, 229, 0.12);
  }

  .optin button {
    width: 100%;
    height: 58px;
    border: 0;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 800;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.2s ease;
  }

  .optin button:hover {
    background: var(--primary-dark);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .privacy {
    margin: 12px 0 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .guide-card {
    width: 360px;
    min-height: 480px;
    padding: 38px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(32, 201, 151, 0.35), transparent 35%),
      linear-gradient(145deg, #10202f, #1e88e5);
    color: var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 34px 90px rgba(16, 32, 47, 0.25);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .guide-card .small {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .guide-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-size: 42px;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  }

  .guide-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.45;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 32px 22px;
    }

    .visual {
      order: -1;
    }

    .guide-card {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 320px;
    }
  }
</style>